title: Top 25 live blog: Tracking Week 1's action from start to finish (VIDEO)
content: The Saturday portion of college football's Week 1 is finally here, and the day kicks off with four games in the early window, highlighted by No. 21 Stanford vs Northwestern. FOX Sports is tracking all of today's Top 25 action here and on our live scoreboard. Alabama vs. Wisconsin is the day's biggest game among 17 Top 25 contests on the schedule. Who you won't see today -- No. 1 Ohio State opens its season Monday night vs. Virginia Tech. Let's light this candle.
